  "text": "Deforestation, expanding agriculture, illegal fishing and hunting, unplanned tourism, and pollution by pesticides have caused a progressive deterioration of natural habitats. Because of the huge demand for soybean plantations, and presently the expansion of sugar-cane, on the upland plateaus surrounding the Pantanal (Planalto), the application of toxic agricultural chemicals is very common [CITATION_1] .",
